  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>通过DvaJs实现redux</title>
    <link href="https://fantasyarcher.github.io/example/Dva%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0redux/"/>
    <id>https://fantasyarcher.github.io/example/Dva实现redux/</id>
    <published>2019-08-21T06:37:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-08-21T07:01:04.223Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-在models中创建文件"><a href="#1-在models中创建文件" class="headerlink" title="1.在models中创建文件"></a>1.在models中创建文件</h2><p><img src="http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/0067JWoSly1g1yoe9xx29j309n05g3yd.jpg" alt="image"><br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="2-配置文件"><a href="#2-配置文件" class="headerlink" title="2.配置文件"></a>2.配置文件</h2><p>基本配置和请求接口时相同<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  namespace: <span class="string">'testList'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  state: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// state中定义变量</span></span><br><span class="line">    testValue: <span class="number">1</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  effects: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 在effects中书写改变变量的方法</span></span><br><span class="line">    * changeTestValue(&#123; payload &#125;, &#123; call, put &#125;) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">yield</span> put(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// type中填入reducers相对应的action方法</span></span><br><span class="line">        type: <span class="string">'getTestValue'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 传入新的数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        payload:payload</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  reducers: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 重新给state中对应变量赋值</span></span><br><span class="line">    getTestValue(state, action) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        ...state,</span><br><span class="line">        testValue: action.payload,</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="3-读取models中的变量"><a href="#3-读取models中的变量" class="headerlink" title="3.读取models中的变量"></a>3.读取models中的变量</h2><ul><li>在页面中引入connect方法</li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; connect &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'dva'</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>绑定state到view</li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@connect(<span class="function">(<span class="params">&#123; testList &#125;</span>) =&gt;</span> (&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  testList,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>读取models中的值</li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">render() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">const</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    testList: &#123; testValue &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125; = <span class="keyword">this</span>.props;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'现在的值：'</span> + testValue);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-更改models中的变量"><a href="#4-更改models中的变量" class="headerlink" title="4.更改models中的变量"></a>4.更改models中的变量</h2><ul><li>在页面中引入connect方法</li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; connect &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">'dva'</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>绑定state到view</li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@connect(<span class="function">(<span class="params">&#123; testList &#125;</span>) =&gt;</span> (&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  testList,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>调用更改方法</li></ul><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">componentDidMount() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    dispatch(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// type为models中reducers里对应的方法</span></span><br><span class="line">    type: <span class="string">'testList/changeTestValue'</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// payload为新传入的数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    payload: <span class="number">2</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h2 id=&quot;1-在models中创建文件&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-在models中创建文件&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1.在models中创建文件&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1.在models中创建文件&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/0067JWoSly1g1yoe9xx29j309n05g3yd.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
